name: Roots
description: This project is growing and taking many forms from M.M.M. to Ganimation to Stills as the condition I'm afflicted with, from satisfaction of creativity to self doubt and desire of changes,Unbridled optimism to Pessimistic outlook . Using what I see through my window looking at the forest I live in to create text prompt, these GAN images created using vqgan-clip are the result of different stages from the burnout I'm currently living. A project meant to get me back to my roots as an artist and a permaculturist.
